p: The title compound was obtained in 37% yield from compound 33 following the general procedure for Suzuki arylation: 1H NMR (300 MHz, CDCl 3) δ 3.91 (s, 3H), 4.65 (s, 2H), 6.56 (d, J = 7.8 Hz, 1H), 6.83 (dd, J = 0.9, 1.8 Hz, 1H), 7.09 (d, J = 8.1 Hz, 1H), 7.33 (t, J = 8.1 Hz, 1H), 7.51 (d, J = 8.4 Hz, 2H), 7.57 (t, J = 1.8 Hz, 1H), 7.91 (s, 1H), 8.01 (d, J = 8.4 Hz, 2H), 8.15 (d, J = 1.8 Hz, 1H), 8.91 (d, J = 2.1 Hz, 1H).
